	   <tr><td colspan=2>Greetings fellow druids, I come before you in a time of need; need for equipment specifically.&nbsp;&nbsp;I am a lv 17 druid of Tunare with about 400 pp to spend.  Here is a list of my current equipment and related stats:<br><br>Ears: 2x Golden Amber Earrings, Str +3<br>Neck: Studded Leather Collar, AC 3, Str +1, Sta +1<br>Face: Leather Mask, AC 2<br>Head: Lumberjack's cap, AC 10, Sta +3<br>Fingers: Silver Opal Engagment ring, Sta +3, Agi +2<br>         Jaded Silver Ring, HP +5, Mana +5<br>Wrists: 2x Small Raw Hide Wristband, AC +3<br>Arms: Ulthrok Hide Arms, AC 8, Dex -3, Wis +3<br>Hands: Leather gloves, AC 4<br>Shoulders: Leather Shoulder Pads, AC 3<br>Chest: Lock Jaw Hide vest, AC 12, Sta +5, Effect: Extended Enhancement I<br>Back: Leather cloak, AC 4<br>Waist: Split Paw HIde Belt, Ac 5, SVP +5<br>Legs: Gnome Skin Leggings, AC 5, SVP +5<br>Feet: Wolf Hide Boots, AC 4<br>Primary: Focused Ethereal Morning Star: Dmg 8, Dly 37, Dex +2, Agi +4<br>Secondary: Shiny Brass Shield, AC 10, SVM +10<br>Range, Ammo: Nothing<br><br>My current gear does not give me much wisdom of which I have great need (I have only 118). But about all of this stuff was given to me, so beggars can't be choosers, lol.  Any comments or suggestions on replacement equipment would be greatly appreciated. Thankyou.  <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
